name: GERM_H
description:
GERM COLLECTION is an alphabet project that is a homage to “Mankind is the germ of this world” Both expresses and symbolizes the cry of the artist against this world that becomes more concrete every day. The project was produced both by hand and digitally. Each letter was first molded and then animated with the stop-motion technique.

Join the fight against this concrete world by owning this NFT and show your inner Germ!
